1. Ona se boj*im da će biti kasno. (She is afraid that it will be late.)
2. Oni su se boj*ali da će biti kažnjeni. (They were afraid to be punished.)
3. On se boj*io da će se izgubiti. (He was afraid to get lost.)
4. Oni su se boj*ali da će biti ranjeni. (They were afraid to be hurt.)
5. On boj*i svoju sobu plavom bojom. (He paints his room blue.)
6. Ona se boj*i da će biti odbijeni. (She is afraid to be rejected.)